      <title>美国核心个人消费支出指数 (PCE) 表现疲弱，12 月消费者支出稳健</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-31/us-core-pce-muted-consumer-spending-solid-in-dec-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储最看重的美国通胀指标，即所谓的核心个人消费支出价格指数，较 11 月小幅上涨 0.2%，而 12 月家庭支出上涨 0.7%。迈克尔·麦基在彭博电视台对这些数据进行了分析。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-31/us-core-pce-muted-consumer-spending-solid-in-dec-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 Jan 2025 14:01:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加密货币交易所 Kraken 称去年收入增长一倍以上</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/crypto-exchange-kraken-says-revenue-more-than-doubled-last-year</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加密货币交易所 Kraken 长期以来一直渴望成为一家上市公司，该公司表示，在去年创纪录的数字资产市场反弹期间，其收入增长了一倍以上。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/crypto-exchange-kraken-says-revenue-more-than-doubled-last-year</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 Jan 2025 13:45:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储鲍曼希望在降息前进一步推动通胀</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/fed-s-bowman-wants-more-inflation-progress-before-cutting-rates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储理事米歇尔鲍曼表示，她希望看到通胀在央行进一步降低利率之前取得更多进展，并质疑在经济强劲的情况下如何实施限制性政策。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/fed-s-bowman-wants-more-inflation-progress-before-cutting-rates</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 Jan 2025 13:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
